  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators will be comparing ultrasound-guided (USG) ankle block and anatomic
      landmark-guided (ALG) ankle block to determine which of these procedures is better in
      surgical anesthesia and in postoperative pain relief.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Not yet recruiting</overall_status>
  <start_date>December 2012</start_date>
